  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Was Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "兰伯尔德太太"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Rumbold a good companion at dinner?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是个很好的宴席同伴吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Last week, at a dinner party, the hostess asked me to sit next to Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "上星期的一次宴会上，女主人让我坐在兰伯尔德太太"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Rumbold.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "旁边。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "兰伯尔德"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Rumbold was a large, unsmiling lady in a tight black dress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "太太身材高大，穿着一件紧身黑连衣裙，脸上毫无笑容。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "She did not even look up when I took my seat beside her.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我在她身边坐下时，她甚至没有抬头看一眼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Her eyes were fixed on her plate, and in a short time, she was busy eating.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她的眼睛紧盯着盘子，很快便忙着吃了起来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "I tried to make conversation.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我试图和她攀谈。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "A new play is coming to the globe soon, I said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“环球剧场不久要上演一出新戏，”我说，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Will you be seeing it?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“您会去看吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "No, she answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“不，”她回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Will you be spending your holidays abroad this year?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“今年您会去国外度假吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "I asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "No, she answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“不，”她回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Will you be staying in England?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“您会留在英国吗？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "I asked.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "No, she answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“不，”她回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "In despair, I asked her whether she was enjoying her dinner.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "绝望之中，我问她是否吃得满意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "Young man, she answered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“年轻人，”她回答，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "If you ate more and talked less, we would both enjoy our dinner.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“如果你多吃点、少说点，我们俩都能把饭吃得更香。”"
      }
    }
  ],
